Learning R through blogging: a journey into the tidyverse

Juillet 07, 2018

I was doing an internship at the Embassy of Switzerland in Guatemala

And missing the cultural life of Geneva

So I started blogging about R

to investigate important questions

Are Marvel movies more successful than the ones of DC Comics?

But taking into account inflation

Which chapter of 1984 is the darkest?

Which countries has James Bond visited?

Which tennis player is the most popular?
